{
  "texts": [
    "To validate and expand our findings, we conducted a snowballing search using the 17 papers linked to the tools as the initial seeds.",
    "Our aim was to identify additional papers associated with a relevant tool.",
    "This search was conducted on Semantic Scholar, foot_3 chosen for its extensive coverage in Computer Science, especially for snowballing searches (Hannousse 2021).",
    "To facilitate this, we developed a custom script to interface with the Semantic Scholar API, enabling the efficient retrieval of references from seed papers and the papers citing them.",
    "5 This process led to the identification of 584 references and 8,009 papers citing the seeds for a total of 8,593 papers."
  ]
}